WEBVTT

00:02.085 --> 00:04.954
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:04.954 --> 00:06.923
(cheering)

00:06.923 --> 00:09.426
(static hissing)

00:09.426 --> 00:10.794
NORM: Hey, wow, Sammy!

00:10.794 --> 00:12.212
Woody, Woody, Woody, jump up there

00:12.212 --> 00:13.213
and fix the TV. again, will you?

00:13.213 --> 00:14.214
(patrons complaining)

00:18.218 --> 00:19.219
Whoa, whoa!

00:19.219 --> 00:20.220
Perfect, Perfect!

00:20.220 --> 00:21.221
Don't move!

00:23.106 --> 00:25.025
Oh, wait a second,
Woody-- uh, just a...

00:25.025 --> 00:27.027
just a minor adjustment.

00:27.027 --> 00:30.030
SAM: That's it!

00:30.030 --> 00:35.035
Oh, I sure hope this game
doesn't go into overtime.

00:35.035 --> 00:38.872
(piano plays)

00:38.872 --> 00:41.324
? Making your way in the world today ?

00:41.324 --> 00:44.327
? Takes everything you've got ?

00:44.327 --> 00:47.330
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

00:47.330 --> 00:50.333
? Sure would help a lot ?

00:50.333 --> 00:55.722
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

00:55.722 --> 00:58.508
? Sometimes you want to go ?

00:58.508 --> 01:03.513
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:03.513 --> 01:08.518
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:08.518 --> 01:11.020
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:11.020 --> 01:13.523
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:13.523 --> 01:19.028
